

Via email, April 2009:

Ph.D. research by Tatiana Bazzichelli:  Networking 2.0. '''An aesthetic, technological and social critique of collective art'''(Aarhus University, Denmark) 


=More Information=

Book, "Networking. The [[Net as Artwork]]. Digital Aesthetics Research Centre, Aarhus University. 

The book describes the evolution of the Italian hacktivism and net culture from the 1980s till today and it is a reconstruction of the history of artistic networking in Italy and of the Italian hacker community.

You can download it from this link: http://darc.imv.au.dk/?p=62

